review_blob: Honostly...this is a beer for those people who are sick of light beers.  There is nothing special about this beer other than the cool label.  If you want a cheap beer with "some" flavor then get yourself some killians irish red.
Honostly...not a real big fan of the stout beer.  However...i can certainly see how a stout drinker would enjoy this beer.  Very dark, creamy, strong tasting beer.

Honostly...I really liked this beer.  The flavor is great, but not strong.  Its got a light, cloudy look to it.  Apparently this beer has good head but I cannot say i saw that.  Good beer though, but not for the money ($11/6 pack).
